patthana9.10:1.1_0: Naāsavaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanoāsavaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana9.10:2.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.10:3.1_0: Nasāsavaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naanāsavaṁ kusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana9.10:4.1_0: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… āsevane ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana9.10:6.1_0: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe cha …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.10:7.1_1: naanāsavañceva nano ca āsavaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca ….
patthana9.10:8.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.10:9.1_1: naāsavavippayuttañceva nano ca āsavaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca ….
patthana9.10:12.1_0: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… āsevane ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
